17:46.246 --> 17:49.178
I was thinking maybe I gave up
on the bangs too quickly.

17:49.795 --> 17:51.019
I don't know.

17:51.054 --> 17:53.522
<i>With graduation looming,</i>
<i>it was just a matter of time</i>

17:53.556 --> 17:56.191
<i>before life sent us</i>
<i>in our own separate directions,</i>

17:56.226 --> 17:58.127
<i>- but for now...</i>
- Lisa!

